Befesa Earning 116.4 Million-Euro Gain Selling Water Arm to Abengoa Unit

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-03-29T06:30:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-29/befesa-earning-116-4-million-euro-gain-selling-water-arm-to-abengoa-unit.html
Befesa Medio Ambiente SA (BMA)  said it
executed an agreement to sell its water engineering business to
Abeinsa, a unit of  Abengoa SA (ABG) , for 144.3 million euros. Befesa
will make a gross capital gain of around 116.4 million euros
from the sale, the company said in a regulatory filing today in
Madrid.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Emma Ross-Thomas at 
 erossthomas@bloomberg.net  